Pin numbers go to esp 32 pinout

LORA RFM95W
  3.3v --> 3.3v
  GND --> GND
  RESET --> 14
  NSS --> 5
  SCK --> 18
  MOSI --> 23
  MISO --> 19

OLED
  VCC --> 3.3v
  GND --> GND
  SCL --> 21
  SDA --> 22

Joystick
  VCC --> 3.3v
  GND --> GND
  x --> 35
  y --> 34

button 1
  -- GND
  -- D12

button 2 
  -- GND
  -- D13

TP4056
  + -- Vin (place a switch between tp4056 + and Vin)
  - -- GND
  B+ --> battery +
  B- --> battery -



  
